songs.title: I Be Killin It

I take your girl cause I be killing it

Boys don’t understand, they too illiterate
Trying to do it like me but I’m too different
Used to be on my ass but now I’m getting it
How the hell you gon' stunt when I don’t fall
All up in your city at the mall

I got these hoes pissed, go to the stall
